---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portrait from '../assets/portrait.jpg';
import family from '../assets/family.jpg';
---

<Layout title="About Tim Dorr | Tim Dorr for Georgia">
  <main class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-balance text-slate-900 uppercase sm:text-5xl">
          Meet Tim Dorr
        </h1>
        <div class="h-2 w-20 rounded-full bg-red-600"></div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 text-slate-400"
      >
        <Image src={portrait} alt="Tim Dorr" class="h-full w-full object-cover object-top" />
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-balance text-slate-900 italic">
          "Georgia is more than just a place to live; it's our community, our home, and our future."
        </p>

        <p>
          Tim Dorr is a dedicated community leader with a passion for public service. He has spent his career
          [Placeholder: professional background, e.g., working in technology and building communities]. Now, he's
          stepping up to represent House District 53 in the Georgia State House.
        </p>

        <h2 class="pt-8 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">A Lifelong Commitment to Georgia</h2>
        <p>
          [Placeholder: Add details about Tim's history in Georgia, his connection to the local community, and specific
          local organizations or initiatives he has been involved with.]
        </p>

        <h2 class="pt-8 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase">Why I'm Running</h2>
        <p>
          [Placeholder: Discuss the core motivation for the campaign. Is it education? Infrastructure? Healthcare?
          Explain the "why" behind the candidacy.]
        </p>

        <p>
          "I believe that we need representatives who are focused on results, not rhetoric. We need a State House that
          works for every Georgian, regardless of their zip code."
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 py-12 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div
            class="flex aspect-square items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 text-slate-400"
          >
            <Image
              src={family}
              alt="Tim Dorr and family"
              class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex aspect-square items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 text-slate-400"
          >
            [Professional/Community Photo]
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
